name: AO 51
description:
They came in peace and now they have been captured! It is up to you to maneuver pass the guards and free our friendly aliens friends.
The task may sound easy, but the area of operation where they are holding our friends is heavily guarded. It will take quick movements to get pass the guards to free them.

Their freedom depends on you. So whatever you do, do not give up!

Sidenotes: If you come in to contact with the enemy, you will be captured. Though the game is over once you come into contact with enemy, the camera will continue going down the game path. It is not a glitch. Press reset to try again. Press pause to see your best score or to return to home page.



Download AO 51 Today!!
